🔧 Troubleshooting
OLED Not Displaying
Check I2C address: 0x3C
Verify GPIO21 (SDA) and GPIO22 (SCL) connections
Use I2C scanner to debug
Current Reading Incorrect
Calibrate ACS712_ZERO_OFFSET_MV if offset differs
Verify ACS712 power supply (5V)
Check GPIO34 ADC connection
Motor Not Starting
Verify 24V power supply (22.8V - 25.2V)
Check relay connections (GPIO12, GPIO13)
Monitor serial output for errors
WiFi Connection Issues
Ensure correct SSID format: MOTOR_CTRL_XXXXXX
Try forgetting network and reconnecting
Check ESP32 antenna connection
Overcurrent Triggered
Reduce current limit setting
Check motor load (may be overloaded)
Verify ACS712 sensor accuracy
